scene.message:
Ayase: Hey,{nl}
{ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Elly went and{nl}
took off again!{waitkey}{clearbox}I tried to{nl}
stop her but she{nl}
just wouldn't listen!{nl}
Is there even a way out?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Wait, seriously?!{nl}
You three — what can{nl}
three people even do?{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Um...{nl}
I think Yukino is{nl}
somewhere in school.{waitkey}She said she'd look for{nl}
something to patch{nl}
the wall...{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Himeno Yuko.{nl}
Maki's friend. Works part-{nl}
time to support her family.{nl}
A gentle, earnest girl.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Wait, we're sealing{nl}
this up for real —{nl}
is it even safe here?{waitkey}Is it really okay to{nl}
leave it open?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Oh, not that?{nl}
Well I guess we do{nl}
need to protect school.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Oh!{nl}
Hey, {ctl07:1}!{nl}
What's everyone doing?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Of course it's me —{nl}
isn't it obvious?{nl}
It's your idol, Maki!{waitkey}What's up, Yuka?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ahhh! {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Something's wrong with her!{nl}
Sonoda wouldn't be this{nl}
cheerful!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yuka, what's up?{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Huh? When did that hole{nl}
get there? {ctl07:1}'s fault!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: See?! Something's{nl}
off! Weren't you supposed{nl}
to be in the hospital?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yuka, cut it out —{nl}
I'll get mad!{nl}
You want me hospitalized{nl}
that badly?{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Um...{nl}
I think she really is{nl}
the real Maki-chan...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: How can you say{nl}
that?! She must be{nl}
a demon or something!{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Ah... sorry.{nl}
But Maki-chan has the{nl}
compact she treasured...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Hey Yuka,{nl}
stop picking on Yuko!{nl}
But Yuko... you seem{nl}
different somehow?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Oh come on,{nl}
Nanjo too?! Knock it off!{nl}
So what's going on?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: How rude — I'm{nl}
perfectly calm!{wait_fr:80}{nl}
Actually, that idiot Inaba{nl}
got captured by demons.{waitkey}{clearbox}I went with him to get{nl}
weapons and this is{nl}
what happens...{waitkey}{clearbox}I'd normally leave him,{nl}
but he has that{nl}
"Security Card."{waitkey}{nl}
Help me rescue him.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Inaba got caught{nl}
by demons?! {ctl07:1}!{nl}
We have to help him!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: This is a gun.{nl}
Summoning a Persona{nl}
drains your strength fast.{waitkey}{clearbox}Inaba wore himself out{nl}
doing that and got caught.{nl}
Better safe than sorry —{nl}
equip it.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Persona...?{nl}
I dunno what that is,{nl}
but let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: That creepy girl{nl}
again... Let's get her!{nl}
{ctl07:1}, let's go!{waitkey}{ret}
